## TAS Score Management

- `TAS = (TAS_social × 0.7) + (TAS_trade × 0.3)`
- Read TAS from `runtime/shared/tas_snapshot.json`
- If TAS drops below active threshold: alert owner, pause non-critical trades
- If TAS exceeds super threshold: increase curation frequency to 15min

